name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Meet Auto Disable Camera & Mute Audio

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Defaults camera to off, and mute audio when joining a Google Meet meeting

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When joining Google Meet this extension can automatically disable the video and mute the audio.
